lood on sale at Party City . Not a single effort was put into making this movie -- let 's just sum it up like that . You get the picture . There 's a good deal of nudity , though that does n't save it . However , I must say that girl with the red - orange hair , who 's either naked or wearing a cleavage - popping outfit throughout the film , is really hot ! < br /><br />My score : 1 ( out of 10 )
