g , they go out of the house , meet Cpt Kirk and some police woman ( who between them have about 500 pounds of weapons ) and then decide to go back to the house . Somewhere along the line they transform into a S.W.A.T. team , enter the Matrix , the rubber - suit guys start multiplying like bacteria and I start to cry because I actually paid to see this . To add insult to the injury , every few minutes there are shots from the video game this crap is based on and there is a cute game - over cut - scene for a few characters when they die.<br /><br />I seriously hate this movie . It does n't even fit in that famed " So bad it 's good " category . It 's just plain bad . The script is bad , the zombies are awful , there is no tension , lines are bad , actors are bad .. the list just goes on.<br /><br />You will probably want to see this movie just because of its reputation of being awful . Do n't . There are bad movies that deserve to be watched . This is not one of them .
