cks out , these guys are driving in a car and the sound of the car changes with every camera angle .... WEAK ! CAMERA : Learn to use it.<br /><br />Anyway , I 'm running out of complaining space ..... rent it - I dare you ... Rent it and learn from it ... give it a 1 rating .. it deserves it.<br /><br />Signing off ... Amanda Christmas
